data.title: Ellie Darcey
data.meta_description: Hello! My name is Randi, and this is a fanblog dedicated to Ellie Darcey-Alden who play's the Young Lily Evans in Harry Potter and The Deathly Hallows Part II. This blog is 100% Harry Potter! ϟ If you...
data.text:
“We have different paths, but the same destiny.”

Hey there!

First off, this is a legitimate giveaway. I am using my own money to purchase the shirt and to pay for the shipping. If you’re going to reblog this with snide comments such as “This is fake, who would do this?” and so on—don’t bother. You’ll only fuck up the number generator and if for some reason your post number was chosen, I’ll simply run the program again to pick a new post number for a new winner. I decided to do this simply because I believe Dramione shippers deserve a treat—an award if you want to call that. We have amazing graphic designers, talented authors, and an amazing fan-base. I myself am not very talented in the graphics department (Still teaching myself PS) and I want to contribute to our fan-base somehow—and I saw this as a good opportunity to do so.

Rules:

You do not have to be following me. Feel free to check out my blog, but following me is not necessary to win this item. I’m not doing this to gain followers.

You can reblog this a maximum of two times—I will check to see how many times you posted this if you’re chosen. I want everyone to have a fair chance, and it’s not exactly fair if you reblogged it 20 times versus someone who only reblogged it twice.

Well this is a bit obvious—You need to be a Dramione shipper. I don’t really see why you’d be interested in this in the first place if you aren’t one.

The deadline is September 30th. I will be drawing a winner October 1st.

This is international. I will be paying for the shipping.

Winner will be selected by a Random Number Generator, the number it generates I will look for the person with that post number. If you and the generator have the same number, you win the shirt.

Likes don’t count. I want as many Dramione shippers as possible to see this & have a chance to win it.

You must have your ask box open. You will have 48 hours to respond. If you don’t respond within 48 hours I will generate a new number and move on.

I might throw some other random goodies in there when I send it, I’m not sure yet so don’t count on it. Just count on the shirt.

Here’s a larger photo of the Shirt:

Once I find a winner, I will ask you your shirt size and order the shirt to ship it to you.

You have the option of four different cut styles:

Scoop Cut:

Fringe Sleeves:

Off the Shoulder:

or Muscle Cut (Sleeveless)

Any questions? Ask me here.

Good luck to all of you!

—Dracosredemption
